The following packages are optional dependencies for salt.
By default, they (and others) may not included in the salt RPMs.
To enable the corresponding functionality within salt, they must be
installed.

MySQL-python
libvirt-python
python-mako
pymongo
python-redis / redis

A list of the optional salt modules (MOCK_MODULES) can be found at
https://github.com/saltstack/salt/blob/develop/doc/conf.py

